  "detailed_description": "Wuhan Clan is a retro inspired pixel art platformer with a modern twist!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay though 25 levels in 5 unique worlds to battle off a virus and save humanity. Along the way you'll face many obstacles and enemies, but with a little help and a variety of weapons to be found you may just be able to overcome them.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFind items and heal the sick to get to the top of the high score. There are many secrets to be found for those curious enough to seek them.",
